text:
President Trump calls extension on mail ballots ‘physically dangerous.' Bay Area faith, labor, and community leaders plan a “Protect Democracy” demonstration in Oakland from 12 to 3 p.m. on Wednesday. 

For more, follow our live updates:

name: sfchronicle
text:
Survivors of wildfires caused by PG&E in 2015, 2017 and 2018 may soon start receiving up to $25,000 they’re owed because of the company’s recent bankruptcy case —the first round of payouts from the estimated $13.5 billion settlement.
